### Skenario 1: Payload valid (harus return 200/201 atau 501 placeholder)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Halo, tes migrasi Next.js 16",
  "user_id": "teguh_test_001"
}

### Skenario 2: Tanpa message (harus return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "teguh_test_001"
}

### Skenario 3: Tanpa user_id (harus return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Cek validasi user"
}
